_sText:
This is my first Gungame map, and I hope you like it!

It has a 'polo' circle in the middle and lots of crates to hide behind on the main ground floor. It also has cool towers on either side to snipe from. These have 4 floors.

It has 21 spawns for CT and 21 for T, totalling up to 42 spawn points.

Thanks for downloading and have fun!
